**Knowledgable Wolf** | Werewolf Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The Knowledgable Wolf knows the role list.
__Details__
At the start of the game the Knowledgable Wolf is told all the roles of the role list.
Alternatively, the hosts may decide to only provide a partial role list.

__Simplified__
The Knowledgable Wolf knows (parts of) the role list.
